{"tid":50292,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【改詞MV】《一個人的聖誕》原：Have yourself a merry little christmas","createTime":"2016-12-22T10:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T18:41:11.000Z","uid":48498,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66205af705579ab7721814dcc601f27f35ee1dc3","tid":50292,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:01:40.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲好，以下係小弟嘅第二首作品《一個人的聖誕》。<br />\n<br />\n舊post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/44505/page/4?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/44505/page/4?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n一直見每年高登聖誕都會有一首聖誕歌，但係到依家都好似未有一首，所以就獻醜寫左一首<br />\n<br />\n原曲係英文歌，Have yourself a merry little christmas,係一首外國經曲嘅聖誕歌，但係香港好似少啲人識佢嘅存在或者會播，但係我就覺得佢好好聽好舒服入耳，雖然英文詞係正面開心，但係好多人之後翻唱嘅版本都有一絲嘅傷感，所以就決定用依首歌改。<br />\n<br />\nYoutube Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PHn-laiTfMU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPHn-laiTfMU&d=C05UyVNISS4Wj7JQRWEtmHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=785cc380\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PHn-laiTfMU</a>"},{"pid":"16a7c887a0359473c146e341610a199abd1d49a2","tid":50292,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:03:15.000Z","msg":"主唱： 羅俊傑 Law Chun Kit<br />\n填詞：大豬包包 Big Piggy Breadbread<br />\n編曲： 羅俊傑 Law Chun Kit<br />\n原曲：have yourself a merry little christmas<br />\nMV:：大豬包包 Big Piggy Breadbread<br />\n圖由於歷史悠久，恕小弟只鳴謝一眾巴絲<br />\n<br />\n來渡節 燈飾比星星更多<br />\n唯獨我 一個<br />\n無落雪 竟好比於冰裏探戈<br />\n<br />\n明月光 映不到骯髒被窩<br />\n留下我 一個<br />\n沿著聽 不想沾污節日興歌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n霜風吹 不走節日氣氛<br />\n卻又留下我 一人<br />\n那會有 天真那勇敢<br />\n明示著我 內心~<br />\n<br />\n無用去 多少的膚淺舞會<br />\n唯獨我 飲醉<br />\n隨大眾 可清醒於美夢 似水<br />\n也許獨個 也可於聖誕夜渡過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n霜風吹 不走節日氣氛<br />\n卻又留下我 一人<br />\n那會有 天真那勇敢<br />\n明示著我 內心~<br />\n<br />\n明月光 映不到骯髒被窩<br />\n留下我 一個<br />\n沿著聽 不想沾污節日興歌<br />\n也許獨個 也可於聖誕夜獨過"},{"pid":"cbde5b6099a68256a11b30a51ef7c13289557e40","tid":50292,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:05:33.000Z","msg":"支持我地嘅巴絲不妨可以Like我地Facebook page同埋聽完留個言，俾下意見<br />\n<br />\n大豬包包<br />\n&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BigPiggyBreadBread/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBigPiggyBreadBread%2F&d=C05UyVNISS4Wj7JQRWEtmHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=6cd78278\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BigPiggyBreadBread/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n羅俊傑Law Chun Kit<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lawchunkitpage/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flawchunkitpage%2F&d=C05UyVNISS4Wj7JQRWEtmHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=c3a6352e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lawchunkitpage/</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : law_chunkit_music"},{"pid":"0e6f0adca632f81905a98f4533965362fa5d1cf5","tid":50292,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:06:00.000Z","msg":"另外特別多謝今次肯唱小弟作品嘅羅俊傑巴打，如果想支持佢，仲可以留意住佢係viuTv個比賽。<br />\n同埋一直支持嘅巴絲，流觴， 凱&bull;， 梁夕， 善莫善於水，記歌詞廢柴，柒叔，雪人巴&hellip;&hellip;不能詳列<br />\n祝大家巴絲聖誕快樂，快啲唔洗一個人過聖誕"},{"pid":"fa1273d98c49e626601faa93ed3687ee62129c3b","tid":50292,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47249f888475b303121cd6d87b33e8ddfb7962a2","tid":50292,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1cd611c571b01a81e736d775024ad1404c4219","tid":50292,"uid":24754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7aaa5aa513f88490894760ce1dea95aabcfd88d","tid":50292,"uid":66909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:07:05.000Z","msg":"霸個靚位先"},{"pid